title: Arbor Whiskey Project :: New Rider - Kyle Smith
description:
You might think that growing up on an island smaller than most cities would limit you, especially being surrounded by the Pacific Ocean, but Kyle Smith has managed to transform the island of Oahu into his own skateboard haven.
 
Destroying rails and ledge
